‚çù SubForm Grid Demo - Tests Grid with embedded components inside SubForm
‚çù Targets: Bug 6 (localStorage race), Grid event coordination, EdgeStyle on Grid

 EWC.SF_EVENT_COUNT‚Üê0

 'F1'eWC'Form' 'SubForm Grid Tests'(50 50)(550 700)('Coord' 'Pixel')

‚çù --- SubForm containing Grid ---
 'F1.SF'eWC'SubForm'('Posn'(10 10))('Size'(490 660))('EdgeStyle' 'Ridge')

‚çù Grid with Edit and Combo columns
 titles‚Üê'Name' 'Score' 'Grade'
 widths‚Üê120 80 80

 'F1.SF.G'eWC'Grid'('ColTitles' titles)('Posn'(10 10))('Size'(200 320))('TitleWidth' 40)('CellWidths' widths)('Event'('CellChanged' 'CellMove')'CBSubFormDemo')('ShowInput' 1)

‚çù Input components for Grid columns
 'F1.SF.G.NAME'eWC'Edit'('Size'(23 120))
 'F1.SF.G.SCORE'eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')('Decimals' 0)('Size'(23 80))
 'F1.SF.G.GRADE'eWC'Combo'('Items'('A' 'B' 'C' 'D' 'F'))('Size'(23 80))

 inputs‚Üê'F1.SF.G.NAME' 'F1.SF.G.SCORE' 'F1.SF.G.GRADE'
 values‚Üê3 3‚ç¥'Alice' '95' 'A' 'Bob' '82' 'B' 'Carol' '71' 'C'

 'F1.SF.G'eWS('Values' values)('CellTypes'(3 3‚ç¥1 1 2))('Input' inputs)
 'F1.SF.G'eWS'CurCell'(1 1)

‚çù Second Grid with EdgeStyle (simpler, no embedded components)
 'F1.SF.L2'eWC'Label' 'Simple Grid with EdgeStyle:'(230 10)(20 250)
 'F1.SF.G2'eWC'Grid'('Posn'(255 10))('Size'(120 200))('EdgeStyle' 'Groove')('CellWidths'(60 60 60))
 'F1.SF.G2'eWS'Values'(3 3‚ç¥'X' 'Y' 'Z' '1' '2' '3' 'A' 'B' 'C')

‚çù Event log inside SubForm
